com.ibm.team.repository.common

Interface IResource

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IInteropProjectAreaDTO, IManagerInfoDTO, IPropertyInfoDTO, ITypeInfoDTO, IVirtual

    public interface IResource
    Base class for addressable resource types

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.lang.String getEtag()
      Returns a unique identifier for this resource that can distinquish a state of this resource instance from any other state of this resource.
      java.lang.String getLocation()
      Returns a location that can identify this resource to the server.

    • Method Detail

      • getLocation

        java.lang.String getLocation()
        Returns a location that can identify this resource to the server. Derivations are required to provide an implementation for this that is compatible with Location.
        Returns:
        The location for identifying this resource. Must not be null.

      • getEtag

        java.lang.String getEtag()
        Returns a unique identifier for this resource that can distinquish a state of this resource instance from any other state of this resource.
        Returns:
        An identifier that distinquishes a state of this resource from all others. May be null if derived resources don't make that distinction.
